snippet.title: Urban Terror - Tɛɛmbø
snippet.description:
Figured I'd release a very last 4.2 fragshow before we finally release our 4.3 baby ;)
So, enjoy the poor quality actions from the rare summer pickups and scrims I played.

♫ Music by Timbeaux (https://soundcloud.com/timbeaux)
